## Configuration

Uses your Linear workflow configuration:

- **Team**: {{linear.teamName}} ({{linear.teamKey}})
- **Hold Status**: Automatically finds status with meaning "paused" or "on hold"
- **Default**: If no hold status exists, keeps current status but adds pause comment

```javascript
// Find "On Hold" status
const onHoldStatus = Object.values(config.linear.statuses).find(s =>
  s.meaning?.includes('paused') ||
  s.meaning?.includes('Hold') ||
  s.name.toLowerCase().includes('hold')
);
```

